import React, { Component } from 'react'; import './about.css'; // import {appendScript} from './random' export default class About extends Component { render() { return (

Sing the Queen City

Welcome Home

Love, Cincy

A Gem of the Midwest

Cincinnati has so much to offer. We can't stop talking about her.

Explore the Seven Hills

Wanderlust Welcome Here

Explore fifty two neighborhoods in our expansive city limits. There is so much to see and experience. Each neighborhood is unique and special with its attractions, businesses, and histories; go on and find your new home away from home.

On the Banks

Down to the River to Play

Cincinnati has beautiful riverfront parks, walkable paths, fun businesses and attractions, and amazing views on the banks of the Ohio River. Enjoy the cool breezes, open air, and some of the best sights Cincinnati has to offer.

Arts & Culture

Sophistication for the Refined Traveler

From Music Hall to our art museums, galleries, theaters, and playhouses, Cincinnat's vibrant arts' scene is alive and well.

Sports and Entertainment

Hey, Batter Batter

Home of the first professional baseball team, the Cincinnati Reds, as well as the Bengals professional football and FC Cincinnati soccer, in addition to our numerous college teams, Cincinnati is ideal for the sports lover.

Love the Outdoors

Unparalled Natural Beauty

From its verdant hills and valleys to shining river, Cincinnati is a natural wonder. The city boasts of numerous public parks with extensive grounds, hiking trails, as well as the largest interconnected biking trails in the United States. Go on, adventure is out there.

Cincinnati Is For Lovers

Romantic Getaways and Wedding Destinations

Make memories for a lifetime here in Cincinnati. With wedding venues to suit all tastes and scenic locations for photographs, Cincinnati is perfect for your dream wedding. Want to get away from it all with your special someone? Look no further than here.
